NAME
    liblog.Log class
DESCRIPTION
    This class is the most basic form of logging.
METHODS
    __init__(filename, display=True)
        Constructor.
        filename: The location where save() should save to.
        display: if true, log() will print to the terminal.
    log(text, log_type="info")
        Log some text to the logfile.
        text: the message to log
        log_type: the type of log.
SEE ALSO
    liblog - the library this class originates from
